        <h3>Client Machines</h3>
        <p>
            An interface for adding and removing client machines that hold our software products.<br />

            <ul>
                <li>Id [int]</li>
                <li>Name [varchar(64)]</li>
                <li>Location [varchar(25)]</li>
                <li>Owner [varchar(30)]</li>
                <li>ITSecurityPlan [varchar(30)] <strong>(optional)</strong></li>
                <li>Active [varchar(10)] <strong>(optional)</strong></li>
            </ul>
        </p>

        <br />

        <h3>Installs</h3>
        <p>
            An interface for adding and removing our current software installations.<br />
            <em>(Dependants: Client Machine, SoftWare License)</em>
            <ul>
                <li>Id [int]</li>
                <li>CM_Id [int]</li>
                <li>SL_Id [int]</li>
                <li>SerialNumber [int] <strong>(optional)</strong></li>
                <li>Comment [text] <strong>(optional)</strong></li>
            </ul>
        </p>

        <br />

